##Client Errors (4xx) â†’ Problem from the client's side.

â¡ï¸400 Bad Request â†’ The request was incorrect.
â¡ï¸401 Unauthorized â†’ Authentication is needed.
â¡ï¸403 Forbidden â†’ Client does not have permission.
â¡ï¸404 Not Found â†’ Requested page does not exist.

##Server Errors (5xx) â†’ Problem on the server.

â¡ï¸500 Internal Server Error â†’ Something broke on the server.
